===Etymology===
From {{L.}} {{term|synonymum|synōnymum|lang=la}} < {{AGr.}} {{term|συνώνυμον|tr=sunōnumon|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}, neuter singular form of {{term|συνώνυμος||synonymous|tr=sunōnumos|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}} < {{term|σύν||with|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}} + {{term|ὄνομα||name|onoma|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}.

